quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  3,42,"Unibuke ubwo abamalayika bavugaga bati “Yewe Mariyamu! Mu by’ukuri, Allah yaragutoranyije (ngo umugandukire), arakweza, anakurutisha abagore bo mu isi (mu gihe cyawe).”"
  3,43,"Yewe Mariyamu! Ibombarike kuri Nyagasani wawe, wubame ndetse ununame (usenga Allah) hamwe n’abunama"
  3,44,Izo ni zimwe mu nkuru z’ibyihishe tuguhishurira (yewe Muhamadi). Kandi ntabwo wari hamwe na bo ubwo banagaga amakaramu yabo (batombora) kugira ngo muri bo haboneke uzarera Mariyamu; ndetse nta n’ubwo wari kumwe na bo ubwo bajyaga impaka
  3,45,"Ibuka ubwo Malayika yavugaga ati “Yewe Mariyamu! Mu by’ukuri, Allah aguhaye inkuru nziza y’ijambo rimuturutseho (ry’uko uzabyara umwana w’umuhungu). Izina rye ni Masihi Issa (Yesu) mwene Mariyamu. Azaba umunyacyubahiro ku isi no ku mperuka, kandi azaba mu bari hafi ya Allah.”"
  3,46,"Azavugisha abantu mu buhinja no mu bukwerere, kandi azaba umwe mu ntungane"
  3,47,"Aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Ni gute nagira umwana kandi nta mugabo wigeze ankoraho?” Aravuga ati “Uko ni ko bimeze, Allah arema icyo ashaka. Iyo aciye iteka ry’ikintu, mu by’ukuri, arakibwira ati “Ba! Ubwo kikaba.”"
  3,48,"Kandi (Allah) azamwigisha igitabo, ubushishozi, Tawurati na Injili (Ivanjili)"
  3,49,"Azanaba Intumwa kuri bene Isiraheli (ababwire) ati “Mu by’ukuri, njye mbazaniye igitangaza giturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu; ndababumbira mu ibumba ikimeze nk’inyoni, ngihuhemo maze gihinduke inyoni ku bushobozi bwa Allah. Ndakiza uwavukanye ubumuga bwo kutabona, umubembe, nzure abapfuye mbishobojwe na Allah, ndetse mbabwire ibyo mwariye n’ibyo muhunitse mu ngo zanyu.” Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ikimenyetso kuri mwe, niba koko muri abemera"
  3,50,"“Kandi naje nshimangira ibyambanjirije biri muri Tawurati, no kugira ngo mbazirurire bimwe mu byo mwari mwaraziririjwe. Ndetse mbazaniye ikimenyetso giturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu. Bityo, nimugandukire Allah munanyumvire.”"
  3,51,"“Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Nyagasani wanjye akaba na Nyagasani wanyu; ku bw’ibyo nimumugaragire (wenyine). Iyo ni yo nzira igororotse.”"
  3,52,"Nuko Issa (Yesu) amaze kubatahuraho ubuhakanyi, aravuga ati “Ni bande banshyigikira mu nzira ya Allah?” Inkoramutima (abigishwa be) baravuga bati “Twe turi abashyigikira (inzira ya) Allah, twemeye Allah kandi unatubere umuhamya ko turi Abayisilamu (abicisha bugufi).”"
  3,53,Nyagasani wacu! Twemeye ibyo wahishuye tunakurikira Intumwa (zawe); bityo twandike mu bahamya (b’ukuri)
  3,54,"Banacuze imigambi mibisha (ubwo abahakanyi bashakaga kwica Issa), Allah na we acura imigambi (yo kuburizamo iyabo). Kandi Allah ni We uhebuje mu kuburizamo imigambi y’abantu babi"